rsor/rules/studio-v2-client-server-isolation.mdc\\n- .cursor/rules/studio-v2-quality.mdc\\n- .cursor/rules/testing-and-quality.mdc\\n- . [... omitted end of long line]","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":15,"content":"{\"type\":\"thinking\",\"subtype\":\"delta\",\"text\":\" V2-IO-8.\",\"session_id\":\"dd5da7ec-5aa4-4eeb-a3ad-17dbb2f5d133\",\"timestamp_ms\":1784784137738}","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":20,"content":"{\"type\":\"thinking\",\"subtype\":\"delta\",\"text\":\" V2-IO-8.\",\"session_id\":\"dd5da7ec-5aa4-4eeb-a3ad-17dbb2f5d133\",\"timestamp_ms\":1784784137740}","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":22,"content":"{\"type\":\"assistant\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"按 prompt 执行 V2-IO-8：先读 skill、执行索引与必读文档。\"}]},\"session_id\":\"dd5da7ec-5aa4-4eeb-a3ad-17dbb2f5d133\",\"model_call_id\":\"7d5a523f-ae64-455e-b049-3e18d53be39c-1-pdfl\",\"timestamp_ms\":1784784137746}","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":23,"content":"[gbx] · 思考 按 prompt 执行 V2-IO-8：先读 skill、执行索引与必读文档。","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":34,"content":"{\"type\":\"tool_call\",\"subtype\":\"completed\",\"call_id\":\"call-11bc799b-90ad-446c-8b52-db2b15230cc4-1\\nfc_e7b47b14-1d56-92a9-9788-b949b3a9cbad_0\",\"tool_call\":{\"readToolCall\":{\"args\":{\"path\":\"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/.cursor/skills/general-batch-exe/SKILL.md\"},\"result\":{\"success\":{\"content\":\"---\\nname: general-batch-exe\\ndescription: >-\\n  External FSM orchestrator for batch Execute–Review–Repair loops via Node CLI\\n  (gbx). Use when the user asks for general-batch-exe, gbx, perfectbatch-ex,\\n  外置批执行, 受控 Ralph, Execute-Review-Repair Loop, or to run an execution index\\n  with --exFile outside the IDE chat. Independent of @batch-execute.\\n---\\n\\n# general-batch-exe（外置批执行编排）\\n\\n用 **独立 Node/JS CLI（`gbx`）** 驱动「执行 → 审查 → 修复 → 验证 → 全量审查」状态机。进度落在执行索引与工作目录文件上，每轮起干净 Agent 上下文。\\n\\n**v0.5.0：** 普通 Fixer 熔断后自动进入阻断分析 → 策略门 → 受限修复 → 复验；任务内问题断点续跑，越界/项目外/gbx 自身问题才人工 BLOCKED。\\n\\n## 独立性（必须）\\n\\n- **不依赖** `.cursor/skills/batch-execute/`（不 import、不调用、不复用其逻辑）。\\n- **不依赖** 宿主仓库 `package.json` / `node_mod [... omitted end of long line]","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":35,"content":"{\"type\":\"tool_call\",\"subtype\":\"completed\",\"call_id\":\"call-11bc799b-90ad-446c-8b52-db2b15230cc4-2\\nfc_e7b47b14-1d56-92a9-9788-b949b3a9cbad_1\",\"tool_call\":{\"readToolCall\":{\"args\":{\"path\":\"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/docs/AI和人类/里程碑/v2.0/引擎存取Port抽象_执行索引.md\"},\"result\":{\"success\":{\"content\":\"---\\n# Studio V2.0 · 引擎存取 Port 抽象执行索引（gbx / general-batch-exe）\\n# 用法：node .cursor/skills/general-batch-exe/bin/gbx.js --exFile <本文件> --workdir <仓库根> [--dry-run]\\n# 本轮目标：引擎存取 Port 协议落地 + 现网 IO 迁入 apps/studioV2/engineIOModule + Host 注入装配 + 文档收口\\nbatch_size: 1\\nmax_rounds: 80\\nmax_fix_attempts: 5\\nmax_ineffective_fixes: 2\\nstop_on_fail: true\\ngroup: order\\n\\nverify_default:\\n  - npm run quality:engine\\n  - npm run quality:studio\\n\\nread_first:\\n  - AGENTS.md\\n  - .cursor/rules/codingRole.mdc\\n  - .cursor/rules/engine-boundaries.mdc\\n  - .cursor/rules/engine-code-quality.mdc\\n  - .cursor/rules/studio-v2-client-server-isolation.mdc\\n  - .cursor/rules/studio-v2-quality.mdc\\n  - .cursor/rules/testing- [... omitted end of long line]","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":38,"content":"{\"type\":\"tool_call\",\"subtype\":\"completed\",\"call_id\":\"call-11bc799b-90ad-446c-8b52-db2b15230cc4-5\\nfc_e7b47b14-1d56-92a9-9788-b949b3a9cbad_4\",\"tool_call\":{\"readToolCall\":{\"args\":{\"path\":\"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/.cursor/rules/engine-code-quality.mdc\"},\"result\":{\"success\":{\"content\":\"---\\ndescription: 引擎代码结构、注释与高风险落点硬规则（本库门禁真源）\\nglobs:\\n  - packages/rpg-engine/**\\n  - scripts/engine-quality/**\\nalwaysApply: false\\n---\\n\\n# 引擎代码质量规则\\n\\n本规则适用于 `packages/rpg-engine` 与引擎质量门禁脚本。机器门禁入口为本库根命令 `npm run quality:engine`（**不在** `general-batch-exe` skill 内实现结构检查）。\\n\\n与 [engine-boundaries.mdc](./engine-boundaries.mdc)（纯度 / Host 边界）互补：本文件管可读性、规模止血与高风险落点声明。\\n\\n## 必须执行\\n\\n- 公共契约、Port、状态转换、幂等 / 事务 / 时序逻辑必须有意图注释或 JSDoc（解释为什么、约束或副作用，禁止复述代码）。\\n- `createEngineHost` / Host 装配层只做装配与会话协调，不新增可独立命名的领域算法；新算法落到 `runtime/`、`schedule/`、`workspace/` 等明确模块。\\n- `effectExecutor` 只做 Effect 调度；复杂 effect 委派 handler / 领域服务，禁止继续无边界堆叠。\\n- Schedule once、recurring、clock、card reference、chapter cleanup 是可分离职责；禁止把新规则只塞 [... omitted end of long line]","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":42,"content":"{\"type\":\"thinking\",\"subtype\":\"delta\",\"text\":\"V2-IO-8 requirements.\",\"session_id\":\"dd5da7ec-5aa4-4eeb-a3ad-17dbb2f5d133\",\"timestamp_ms\":1784784140543}","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":46,"content":"{\"type\":\"tool_call\",\"subtype\":\"started\",\"call_id\":\"call-0b6bf26f-7f28-459d-b809-7751cdf292e3-6\\nfc_5152aa0c-1657-9fa0-aa3b-3ad041e8903f_0\",\"tool_call\":{\"grepToolCall\":{\"args\":{\"pattern\":\"validate|ContentPort|V2-IO-8|读盘\",\"path\":\"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/docs/AI和人类/里程碑/v2.0/引擎存取Port抽象_需求.md\",\"caseInsensitive\":false,\"multiline\":false,\"toolCallId\":\"call-0b6bf26f-7f28-459d-b809-7751cdf292e3-6\\nfc_5152aa0c-1657-9fa0-aa3b-3ad041e8903f_0\",\"offset\":0}},\"hookAdditionalContexts\":[],\"toolCallId\":\"call-0b6bf26f-7f28-459d-b809-7751cdf292e3-6\\nfc_5152aa0c-1657-9fa0-aa3b-3ad041e8903f_0\",\"startedAtMs\":\"1784784140645\"},\"model_call_id\":\"7d5a523f-ae64-455e-b049-3e18d53be39c-2-8arb\",\"session_id\":\"dd5da7ec-5aa4-4eeb-a3ad-17dbb2f5d133\",\"timestamp_ms\":1784784140550}","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":47,"content":"[gbx] · 搜索 validate|ContentPort|V2-IO-8|读盘 in docs/AI和人类/里程碑/v2.0/引擎存取Port抽象_需求.md","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":50,"content":