ta.uri}`,\\n\\t\\t\\t});\\n\\t\\t}\\n\\t}\\n\\n\\tif (opts.checkKindForPlayback && !PLAYBACK_ASSET_KINDS.has(meta.kind)) {\\n\\t\\tpush(warnings, {\\n\\t\\t\\truleId: \\\"ASSET_KIND_MISMATCH\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\tlevel: \\\"warning\\\",\\n\\t\\t\\tpath: issuePath,\\n\\t\\t\\tmessage: `playback/system clip ${assetId} has kind ${meta.kind}`,\\n\\t\\t});\\n\\t}\\n}\\n\",\"message\":\"Wrote contents to /Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/packages/rpg-engine/src/validation/validatePackageAssets.ts\"}}},\"hookAdditionalContexts\":[],\"toolCallId\":\"call-b85c1753-0c99-4edf-bad8-e9d50357f319-73\\nfc_d8e33abf-d270-914f-bf1f-4d47e96a07cc_0\",\"startedAtMs\":\"1784784378346\",\"completedAtMs\":\"1784784378790\"},\"model_call_id\":\"7d5a523f-ae64-455e-b049-3e18d53be39c-25-m8gp\",\"session_id\":\"dd5da7ec-5aa4-4eeb-a3ad-17dbb2f5d133\",\"timestamp_ms\":1784784378686}\n921:{\"type\":\"tool_call\",\"subtype\":\"completed\",\"call_id\":\"call-b85c1753-0c99-4edf-bad8-e9d50357f319-74\\nfc_d8e33abf-d270-914f-bf1f-4d47e96a07cc_1\",\"tool_call\":{\"editToolCall\":{\"args\":{\"path\":\"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/packages/rpg-engine/src/validation/validatePackageSchedule.ts\",\"streamContent\":\"/**\\n * 模块名称：validatePackage 调度 Effect 规则\\n * 模块说明：从 validatePackage 拆出以降复杂度基线；读卡经 ContentPort。\\n */\\nimport { FREE_PACKAGE_ID, SCHEDULE_PACKAGE_ID } from \\\"../constants.js\\\";\\nimport type { ContentPort } from \\\"../ports/contentPort.js\\\";\\nimport type { CallCardDefinition } from \\\"../schema/callCard.js\\\";\\nimport type { ValidationIssue } from \\\"./types.js\\\";\\n\\nfunction push(list: ValidationIssue[], issue: ValidationIssue): void {\\n\\tlist.push(issue);\\n}\\n\\n/** SCHEDULE_ONCE_CARD_REQUIRED：延迟外呼必须 agentId+packageId+cardId */\\nexport function validateScheduleOnceEffect(\\n\\teffect: { id: string; effect: string; [key: string]: unknown },\\n\\tissuePath: string,\\n\\terrors: ValidationIssue[],\\n): void {\\n\\tconst agentId = typeof effect.agentId === \\\"string\\