ong line]","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":37,"content":"{\"type\":\"tool_call\",\"subtype\":\"completed\",\"call_id\":\"call-2dca10eb-df93-4e95-88b9-e0a49208b54d-4\\nfc_9baf1970-d352-9371-8f35-56c1956db8d2_3\",\"tool_call\":{\"readToolCall\":{\"args\":{\"path\":\"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/.cursor/rules/engine-boundaries.mdc\"},\"result\":{\"success\":{\"content\":\"---\\ndescription: packages/rpg-engine 纯引擎边界\\nglobs: packages/rpg-engine/**\\nalwaysApply: false\\n---\\n\\n# 引擎包边界（rpg-engine）\\n\\n详情：[05](../../docs/AI和人类/技术设计文档/05-技术选型与工程边界.md)、[19](../../docs/AI和人类/技术设计文档/19-引擎宿主与会话模型.md)、[02](../../docs/AI和人类/需求/02-运行时协议.md)。\\n\\n## 必须执行\\n\\n- **禁止** import：`react`、`react-dom`、`next`、`@xyflow/*`。\\n- **禁止** `window` / `document` / `localStorage`（测试可注入）。\\n- **EngineHost 单例**由 server/壳持有；本包提供 create/host API。\\n- **CallSession** 在 Host 内存；`frozenCard`；同 user 通话互斥。\\n- Composer 只读；EffectExecutor 仅出口/Free 管线；工具只登记 candidate。\\n- **FreeCallPostPipeline** 为 Free 挂机唯一总入口（可注入）；v1 = 有效门闩 + MemoryCommit +（有 candidate 则 ExitSelector）；禁 transcript 隐式扫描。\\n- Free Session.`packageId = [... omitted end of long line]","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":38,"content":"{\"type\":\"tool_call\",\"subtype\":\"completed\",\"call_id\":\"call-2dca10eb-df93-4e95-88b9-e0a49208b54d-3\\nfc_9baf1970-d352-9371-8f35-56c1956db8d2_2\",\"tool_call\":{\"readToolCall\":{\"args\":{\"path\":\"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/.cursor/rules/docs-execution.mdc\"},\"result\":{\"success\":{\"content\":\"---\\ndescription: 编码前读什么 doc、变更后写哪\\nglobs: docs/**,packages/**,apps/**\\nalwaysApply: false\\n---\\n\\n# 文档执行规范\\n\\n与 [docs-governance.mdc](./docs-governance.mdc)、[规则制定原则.mdc](./规则制定原则.mdc) 衔接。\\n\\n**冲突裁决**：当前代码/测试 > `codingRole.mdc` > 本规范 > `docs/AI/` > `docs/AI和人类/技术设计文档/`（工程）≈ `docs/AI和人类/需求/`（产品）> `docs/人类/`。产品「做什么」与工程「怎么落」冲突时先对齐用户。\\n\\n## 编码前最小阅读集\\n\\n| 任务类型 | 必读 |\\n|----------|------|\\n| **任意非 trivial** | [AGENTS.md](